---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Contact
description: Contact the MACS Cushman Cabin — phone, email, and inquiry form.
permalink: /contact/
---
<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">Say Hello</p>
    <h1>Contact</h1>
    <p>Questions about the cabin, your stay, or the area? We're locals — ask away.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="section">
  <div class="wrap contact-grid">
    <div>
      <h2>Reach us directly</h2>
      <ul class="contact-list mt-4">
        <li>
          <strong>Phone</strong>
          <a href="tel:+12532546862">{{ site.phone }}</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Email</strong>
          <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>The Cabin</strong>
          {{ site.address.street }}<br>{{ site.address.city }}, {{ site.address.state }} {{ site.address.zip }}
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Follow along</strong>
          <a href="{{ site.social.facebook }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Facebook</a> ·
          <a href="{{ site.social.instagram }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2>Send an inquiry</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">Planning a stay and want to check something first — group size, boat passes, longer stays? Use the inquiry form and we'll get back to you.</p>
      <p class="mt-2"><a class="btn btn--ghost" href="{{ site.inquiryFormUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-analytics="inquiry_form_click">Open Inquiry Form ↗</a></p>
      <p class="muted mt-4">Ready to book? Head straight to <a href="/book/">reservations</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
